---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Community Guidelines - Lobbi">
  <main>
    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 header-blur">
      <div class="header-container">
        <a href="/" class="header-logo-link">
          <img src="/lobbi-logo-transparent.png" alt="Lobbi" class="header-logo" />
        </a>
        <a href="/" class="back-link">← Back to Home</a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Content -->
    <section class="legal-content">
      <div class="legal-container">
        <h1 class="legal-title">COMMUNITY GUIDELINES</h1>
        
        <p class="legal-intro">
          Welcome to Lobbi, a space created for mature gamers – especially parents and busy adults – to find gaming partners who play the same games on a similar schedule. To keep this community safe, respectful, and enjoyable for everyone, please follow the guidelines below. Violations may result in warnings, feature limitations, or account removal.
        </p>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>COMMUNITY EXPECTATIONS</h2>
          
          <h3>Respect & Kindness</h3>
          <p>
            Engage with others respectfully. We're here to build genuine connections and because most of us are working with very limited (and very precious) gaming time, we rely on patience, respect, and clear communication to keep things running smoothly.
          </p>
          
          <h3>Authenticity</h3>
          <p>
            Create an honest profile and interact as your real self. Accurate profile details help match you with compatible users and ensure a trustworthy environment.
          </p>
          
          <h3>Positive, Supportive Interactions</h3>
          <p>
            Share experiences, coordinate play sessions and communicate clearly. If you need to reschedule or step away, be direct rather than disappearing.
          </p>
          
          <h3>Constructive Communication</h3>
          <p>
            We know gaming debates can get spicy and some light trash talk comes with the territory. Just keep it fun, not personal.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>PROHIBITED CONTENT & BEHAVIORS</h2>
          
          <h3>Impersonation & Misrepresentation</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Do not impersonate other people or create fake identities.</li>
            <li>Use only your own photos and information.</li>
            <li>Shared or duplicate accounts are not allowed.</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h3>Misinformation</h3>
          <p>
            Content that is false, misleading, or harmful – including misinformation about health, safety, or identity – is not permitted.
          </p>
          
          <h3>Intellectual Property Violations</h3>
          <p>
            Only share content you own or have permission to use. Posting or distributing copyrighted work without authorization is prohibited.
          </p>
          
          <h3>Hate Speech & Discrimination</h3>
          <p>We do not allow content or behavior that attacks, demeans, or encourages harm toward individuals or groups based on:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Race</li>
            <li>Ethnicity</li>
            <li>Religion</li>
            <li>Sexual orientation</li>
            <li>Disability</li>
            <li>Gender identity or expression</li>
            <li>Age</li>
            <li>Nationality</li>
            <li>Socioeconomic status</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h3>Harassment, Bullying, or Threats</h3>
          <p>Strictly prohibited, including:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Intimidation, insults, or hostile behavior</li>
            <li>Repeated unwanted messages</li>
            <li>Sharing or threatening to share personal information (doxxing)</li>
            <li>Posting screenshots of private conversations without permission</li>
            <li>Pressuring others into playing or responding</li>
            <li>Abusive behavior in voice or text chats</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h3>False Reporting</h3>
          <p>
            Misusing the reporting system, including retaliatory or intentionally false reports, is not allowed.
          </p>
          
          <h3>Sexual or Inappropriate Content</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>No nudity, pornography, sexual messages, or sexual solicitation.</li>
            <li>Any content involving minors that is abusive, exploitative, or sexualized is strictly prohibited.</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h3>Illegal Activities</h3>
          <p>The app cannot be used to engage in or facilitate unlawful behavior, including (but not limited to):</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Fraud, scams, or theft</li>
            <li>Selling or distributing prohibited items</li>
            <li>Buying/selling accounts, hacks, or in-game goods in ways that violate law or game TOS</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h3>Advertising, Solicitation & Self-Promotion</h3>
          <p>The platform is for genuine connections. The following are not allowed:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Selling products or services</li>
            <li>Promoting personal businesses, streams, or affiliate links</li>
            <li>Requests for money or fundraising</li>
            <li>Recruitment for MLMs or any affiliate-based groups</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h3>Prohibited Use of the Platform</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Do not use the app to initiate romantic or sexual interactions.</li>
            <li>Do not attempt to scrape data, automate interactions, or exploit features.</li>
            <li>Do not collect information about users for any purpose outside gameplay coordination.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>KEEPING THE COMMUNITY SAFE</h2>
          <p>
            If you encounter behavior or content that violates these Guidelines, please report it directly through the app. Your reports help maintain a safer and more enjoyable experience for everyone.
          </p>
          <p>
            For questions about these Guidelines or our reporting process, visit our <a href="/faq">FAQs</a> or <a href="mailto:support@lobbiapp.com">contact support</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .header-blur {
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    background: rgba(13, 17, 23, 0.8);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  }

  .header-container {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 16px 24px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .header-logo-link {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .header-logo {
    height: 32px;
    width: auto;
  }

  .back-link {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .legal-content {
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 140px 24px 80px;
    background: var(--color-background);
  }

  .legal-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .legal-title {
    font-family: 'Clash Display', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
  }

  .legal-intro {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    padding-bottom: 24px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .legal-section {
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .legal-section h2 {
    font-family: 'Clash Display', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    padding-bottom: 12px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-primary);
  }

  .legal-section h3 {
    font-family: 'Clash Display', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-top: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .legal-section p {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .legal-section ul {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin: 12px 0 16px;
    padding-left: 24px;
    list-style-type: disc;
  }

  .legal-section li {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .legal-section a {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
  }

  .legal-section a:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .legal-section strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
</style>

